{"tid":462961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"估佢唔到！民建聯及工聯會憂再現奶粉搶購潮　政府總部外請願反撤限奶令","createTime":"2017-11-09T05:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T02:40:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"46973bf734add26611ca2e70a14a01a5f48fe6ea","tid":462961,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1363832_1_20171109105900.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1363832_1_20171109105900.jpg&h=e9d88456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1363832-20171109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1363832-20171109.htm&d=jSwC3uiGN3vC7JBO22xqb7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=dd8158c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1363832-20171109.htm&h=075fdd37\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1363832-20171109.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會第二日辯論施政報告致謝議案，民建聯及工聯會到政府總部外請願，因應施政報告建議檢討「限奶令」，他們擔心會再出現奶粉搶購潮。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員劉國勳表示，很多市民擔心放寬限奶令，加上內地放寬一孩政策，一旦令奶粉需求增加，會加劇北區水貨問題及導致本地奶粉供應短缺。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯建議政府將配方奶粉納入《儲備商品條例》之內，令政府可隨時監察供應商的存貨量，並公開信息，減少搶購奶粉行為。"},{"pid":"d7931affa9bc6a28c67b233ec57711766a6cbe91","tid":462961,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:12:19.000Z","msg":"佢地獨市丫ma 佢地運幾多上去"},{"pid":"87c6f5b0add281d1a7a4f6b482a3bb2bbb9a9642","tid":462961,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:15:03.000Z","msg":"補選近了"},{"pid":"527e879534fb0835465ee29a03a00b3f0bc62a20","tid":462961,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:21:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地獨市丫ma 佢地運幾多上去</blockquote><br />\n正解"},{"pid":"41e860367b63dd96c24ff957291de8405d7f6fc8","tid":462961,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}